components.queue

Class QueueSecondary<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • components.queue.QueueCommon<T>
      • components.queue.QueueSecondary<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of Queue entries
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Queue<T>, QueueKernel<T>, components.standard.Standard<Queue<T>>, Iterable<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Queue1L, Queue2

    public abstract class QueueSecondary<T>
extends QueueCommon<T>
    Layered implementations of secondary methods for Queue.

    Execution-time performance of append and flip implemented in this class is O(|this|). Execution-time performance of sort implemented in this class is O(|this| log |this|) expected, O(|this|^2) worst case.
